    <PreviewImage>Data/Images/arena_editor/full.jpg</PreviewImage>
    <Description>Adds a user friendly arena editor like in previous alphas. To use go into an arena level an find an arena battle object (two green crossed swords with a green circle behind them). Selecting it will bring up the arena editor.

If you want to make your own arena levels you can refer to https://youtu.be/S-H7P6tmCAc?t=90 this video.
    </Description>
    <Version>1.0.3</Version>
    <Author>DoctorGester</Author>
    <Tag>Editor</Tag>
    <Tag>Script</Tag>
    <SupportedVersion>*</SupportedVersion>
    <NeedsRestart>false</NeedsRestart>
    <LevelHookFile>Data/Scripts/arena_editor/arena_editor.as</LevelHookFile>
</Mod>
